Output demos/inline-loading.gif
Set FontSize 28
Set Width 1100
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Padding 10
Set Framerate 60

Hide
Type "cd layoutz-hs && cabal build inline-loading-demo"
Enter
Sleep 30s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "cabal run inline-loading-demo"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 12s

Hide
